uant_weights (optional)"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"fused_mod","name":"fused_mod","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"fused_mod"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"manual_unload_model","name":"manual_unload_model","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"manual_unload_model"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"pipeline","name":"pipeline","type":"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE","links":[13]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"QuantFuncModelLoader"},"widgets_values":["path/to/base_models/or/diffuser_models","path/to/prequant_models.safetensors","lighting",0,"",""," "," ",false,false]},{"id":14,"type":"Note","pos":[-420.15661579388626,1213.8664858777981],"size":[320.6862347400988,389.97565870289117],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"使用前阅","properties":{},"widgets_values":["本工作流专用于对 qwen-edit（图生图）系列 Transformer 进行实时量化运行。注意：此场景下不会导出模型，通常用于测试模型与 LoRA 的整合效果。使用前需配置以下参数：\n\n@model_dir：diffusers 格式的模型路径。\n\n@transformer_path：若使用 lighting 模型，此项留空；若使用 svdq 模型，需填入预量化 Transformer 权重路径，例如 path/to/transformer/qwen-image-2511-50x-above-lighting-4steps.safetensors。\n\n@model_backend：必须与当前 Transformer 的模型类型严格对应，可选值为 svdq 或 lighting。\n\n@precision_config（仅 lighting）：需额外指定精度配置文件路径，用于逐层设定精度，具体填写方式请参考官网。\n\n#LoRA 使用说明#\n\n@svdq 模式下使用 LoRA 时，必须添加 LoRA Config 节点，用于控制新 LoRA 与 svdq 中已有 LoRA 的组合方式。\n\n@推荐使用 ROP 算法——这是我们的创新算法，可先找到多个 LoRA 之间通用的 rank，再以能量损失最小为目标进行截断。\n\n@lighting 模式下使用 LoRA 时，无需添加任何 Config 节点，lighting 会直接将 LoRA 权重与模型权重相加融合。"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653","shape":"round"},{"id":15,"type":"Note","pos":[-421.6995519281969,1646.7801727973601],"size":[322.5284671464872,529.4024985577948],"flags":{},"order":12,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Readme","properties":{},"widgets_values":["This workflow is designed for real-time quantization and execution of qwen-edit (image-to-image) series Transformer models. Note: no model will be exported in this mode. It is typically used for testing the integration effects between models and LoRA. The following parameters must be configured:\n\n@model_dir: Path to the model in diffusers format.\n\n@transformer_path: Leave empty if using a lighting model. If using svdq, provide the path to the pre-quantized Transformer weight file, e.g. path/to/transformer/qwen-image-2511-50x-above-lighting-4steps.safetensors.\n\n@model_backend: Must strictly match the model type of the Transformer being used. Valid options are svdq or lighting.\n\n@precision_config (lighting only): An additional precision config file path is required to specify the precision of each layer. Please refer to the official documentation for details.\n\n#LoRA Usage Notes#\n\n@In svdq mode, a LoRA Config node must be attached to control how the new LoRA combines with the existing LoRA inside svdq.\n\n@We recommend using the ROP algorithm — our proprietary innovation that first identifies the shared rank across multiple LoRAs, then truncates based on minimum energy loss.\n\n@In lighting mode, no Config node is needed. Lighting directly merges LoRA weights into the model weights by addition."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653","shape":"round"},{"id":17,"type":"QuantFuncGenerate","pos":[1212.210110523974,1265.5846490294905],"size":[624.669130803371,341.7789348129254],"flags":{},"order":21,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"pipeline","name":"pipeline","type":"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE","link":10},{"localized_name":"ref_images","name":"ref_images","shape":7,"type":"QUANTFUNC_IMAGE_LIST","link":11},{"localized_name":"prompt","name":"prompt","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"prompt"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"width","name":"width","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"width"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"height","name":"height","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"height"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"steps","name":"steps","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"steps"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"seed","name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"guidance_scale","name":"gui